      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1994061559,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 2016439737,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772529490185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "VIDEO FILE (MP4)\n      ↓\n1. EXTRACT FRAMES using FFmpeg\n   (pick 10 random frames from the video)\n      ↓\n2. SAVE FRAMES to /tmp\n   /tmp/job_123/frame_001.jpg\n   /tmp/job_123/frame_002.jpg\n   ...\n      ↓\n3. READ FRAMES and send to AI\n   (Google Gemini / GPT-4 Vision)\n      ↓\n4. AI ANALYZES all frames\n   Returns: Restaurant name, food type, location\n      ↓\n5. CLEANUP /tmp files\n      ↓\n6. SAVE RESULTS to database\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "VIDEO FILE (MP4)\n      ↓\n1. EXTRACT FRAMES using FFmpeg\n   (pick 10 random frames from the video)\n      ↓\n2. SAVE FRAMES to /tmp\n   /tmp/job_123/frame_001.jpg\n   /tmp/job_123/frame_002.jpg\n   ...\n      ↓\n3. READ FRAMES and send to AI\n   (Google Gemini / GPT-4 Vision)\n      ↓\n4. AI ANALYZES all frames\n   Returns: Restaurant name, food type, location\n      ↓\n5. CLEANUP /tmp files\n      ↓\n6. SAVE RESULTS to database\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "v1rxGEyp9QETWSx9vKc9M",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 346.1540832519531,
      "y": 2536.1050892028834,
      "width": 507.91973876953125,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1881318719,
      "version": 160,
      "versionNonce": 13371039,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729170895,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2) How do we support resumable uploads?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2) How do we support resumable uploads?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "jZiZtYZ1cTS3Ctmr3zKEm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 346.254150390625,
      "y": 2613.2751346740747,
      "width": 439.7397155761719,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 347378225,
      "version": 203,
      "versionNonce": 1278776287,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729154442,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In order to support resumable uploads for\nlarger videos, we'll need to consider how we'll\ntrack progress for the video upload flow. Of\nnote, this refers to tracking progress of the\noriginal upload.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In order to support resumable uploads for larger videos, we'll need to consider how we'll track progress for the video upload flow. Of note, this refers to tracking progress of the original upload.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0mUf-kaz5yORJGrlJX7I1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 356.0141143798828,
      "y": 2779.215106597903,
      "width": 407.499755859375,
      "height": 64.80000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 161817617,
      "version": 82,
      "versionNonce": 1826360945,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729250101,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The client would divide the video file into chunks, each\nwith a fingerprint hash. A chunk would be small, ~5-\n10MB in size.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The client would divide the video file into chunks, each with a fingerprint hash. A chunk would be small, ~5-10MB in size.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "DO8aKVePCSIF4JJ1NcMFt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 359.25413513183594,
      "y": 2860.5651127014185,
      "width": 393.939697265625,
      "height": 64.80000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 700162431,
      "version": 127,
      "versionNonce": 765347537,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729252989,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "VideoMetadata would have a field called chunks\nwhich would be a list of chunk JSONs, each with\nfingerprint and status field.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "VideoMetadata would have a field called chunks which would be a list of chunk JSONs, each with fingerprint and status field.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "SRKrYCEVbodlXcWBcXojQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 358.42417907714844,
      "y": 2944.750095001223,
      "width": 427.5797119140625,
      "height": 64.80000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 443054577,
      "version": 168,
      "versionNonce": 44959985,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729254605,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The client would POST request to the backend to update\nthe VideoMetadata with the list of chunks, each with\nstatus NotUploaded.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The client would POST request to the backend to update the VideoMetadata with the list of chunks, each with status NotUploaded.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "KvsBiPWblMC8R1JXE_jTR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 353.75413513183594,
      "y": 3033.4051120910667,
      "width": 306.57574462890625,
      "height": 21.6,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2045319583,
      "version": 136,
      "versionNonce": 410655057,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729290253,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The client would upload each chunk to S3.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The client would upload each chunk to S3.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "pJANXzbd0ZnDNoGwISA9C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 349.54417419433594,
      "y": 3077.1051517639185,
      "width": 419.1197509765625,
      "height": 108,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1208357841,
      "version": 160,
      "versionNonce": 8074929,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729266268,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When S3 acknowledges a part upload it returns the part\nnumber and an ETag. The client relays that response to\nthe backend (e.g. PATCH /videos/{id}/chunks) so the server\ncan verify the fingerprint/ETag via S3 APIs and then\nupdate the matching chunk record to Uploaded.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When S3 acknowledges a part upload it returns the part number and an ETag. The client relays that response to the backend (e.g. PATCH /videos/{id}/chunks) so the server can verify the fingerprint/ETag via S3 APIs and then update the matching chunk record to Uploaded.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "SNL42Vr3W7a-oVJSx3Loo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 349.01414489746094,
      "y": 3211.205096832278,
      "width": 424.0196533203125,
      "height": 129.60000000000002,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 837979583,
      "version": 172,
      "versionNonce": 234306463,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729274857,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once the client calls CompleteMultipartUpload, S3 emits\nan object-level notification (e.g.\nObjectCreated:CompleteMultipartUpload) exactly once\nper object. That single event can kick off downstream\nprocessing, but chunk-level progress tracking remains\nclient-driven as described above.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once the client calls CompleteMultipartUpload, S3 emits an object-level notification (e.g. ObjectCreated:CompleteMultipartUpload) exactly once per object. That single event can kick off downstream processing, but chunk-level progress tracking remains client-driven as described above.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ZMEIGpcitEe-2vuo5Qz0p",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 339.49412536621094,
      "y": 3367.63019143677,
      "width": 423.19970703125,
      "height": 64.80000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 110457265,
      "version": 151,
      "versionNonce": 207751633,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772729283956,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If the client stops uploading, it can resume by fetching the\nVideoMetadata to see the uploaded chunks and to skip\nchunks that had been uploaded already",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If the client stops uploading, it can resume by fetching the VideoMetadata to see the uploaded chunks and to skip chunks that had been uploaded already",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "31Sd-DRcY3YRjBCND2N9j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 454.5240173339844,
      "y": 3501.455149505618,
      "width": 183.59988403320312,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 502653932,
      "version": 118,
      "versionNonce": 1684381804,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800537371,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Raw Video (1 hour)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
